</div>
<div id="p4" class="ltx_para">
<p class="ltx_p">We have explicit font shape/weight for alphabetic tokens when they look like text, compare <math id="p4.m1" class="ltx_Math" alttext="a" display="inline"><semantics><mi>a</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun">italic_a</annotation></semantics></math> to <math id="p4.m2" class="ltx_Math" alttext="\mathrm{a}" display="inline"><semantics><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><annotation encoding="application/x-llamapun">roman_a</annotation></semantics></math>.
